title: Beef Salpicao
summary: Beef Salpicao is quick beef stir-fry with garlic. Easy to make and full of flavor. it's delicious as an appetizer but easily doubles as a main dish.

title: Rellenong Alimango
summary: Rellenong Alimango is a baked stuffed crab shell with delicious crab meat and tender veggies. Try this show-stopping dish for a special meal.

title: Pinsec Frito
summary: Pinsec Prito are Asian dumplings fried to perfection and served with sweet and sour sauce. They're crispy, tasty, and sure to be a hit with guests of all ages!

title: Banana Heart Burger

summary: Looking for a sweet, savory BBQ recipe? These baby-back pork ribs with adobo glaze are fall-off-the-bone tender. A must-try recipe that everyone will enjoy!

summary: Filipino Pork Barbecue are made of pork slices marinated in a sweet BBQ sauce and skewered in bamboo sticks. Sweet, salty, and slightly spicy, these Filipino-style meat kebabs are seriously addictive!

title: Camaron Rebosado
summary: Camaron Rebosado is a Filipino dish made of large shrimp dipped in batter and deep-fried to golden perfection. Delicious as an appetizer or main dish with your favorite dipping sauce!

title: Ukoy na Dilis

title: Kwek-kwek

Loslos are easy to make and delicious as an appetizer or main dish. Golden, crunchy, and bursting with adobo flavors, these pork ribs are sure to be a crowd-pleaser.
